				<td colspan="2"><span>I would guess you mean AE kiting -- swarm kiting and chant kiting aren't that difficult to maintain range outside melee radius.  Our AEs, by contrast, are seldom significantly wider range than melee on mobs which makes it very hard to master.  The payoff is huge if you can master it, but it just isn't easy.</span></td>
