				<td colspan="2"><span>I basically Autorun (numlock) and press my left arrow in a rhythmic fashion, on and off.  You don't make a &quot;perfect circle&quot; but who cares?  How often you press the arrow key depends on your speed relative to the mobs, and how close you need to be to them.  (REAL close for AE kiting, VERY comfortable and safe distance for Chant Kiting, or single-mob Charm/Chant Kiting).</span></td>
