				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: OK not so noob to EQ but cannot figure out kiting... Retired BL<a name="38107"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">May 4 04 1:38 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>It's very simple
<br />
press and HOLD <b>both</b> the up and left/right (your choice) arrow keys.  At this point you will be running in a circle, the exact same size as when this finishes.
<br />

<br />
Now, press the [ENTER] key and RELEASE(let go of) all THREE (3) at the same time.  You should now be running without holding any keys.  Mind you, at this point you have a blinking chat cursor, so press enter again before you start to twist.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
